snippet.title: "Lynette: Cat in the Box" Piano Cover | Genshin Impact Character Demo OST
snippet.description:
Genshin Impact - Lynette Demo 「Cat in the Box」 OST Piano Performance


Finally, the new continent "Fontaine" has arrived!!

Fontaine's characteristic Lynette waiting in the "Footsteps PV"!!
Appears as the first pickup character in 4.0 along with Lyney

I like it as much as I have been waiting for a long time.
Concept, visual, motion, everything!!
What's more, she is distributed for free, so anyone can use her, it's really great!!

I also really like Lynette's character theme music.
It reminds me of "Collei", which first appeared as a pickup in Sumeru.
So I tried arranging and playing with a similar feeling.

Thank you for listening.

---------------------------------------------------
Discord Channel : https://discord.gg/TGvwJR9rs7
Twitch Streaming : https://www.twitch.tv/frost_piano
---------------------------------------------------
Nilou's 'Dance of Sabzeruz' Piano Performance : https://youtu.be/Ab97Db-3FiU
Aranara's Theme Piano Performance : https://youtu.be/YJtCY1zp94Y
'Dori' theme Insane Piano Duet Performance : https://youtu.be/7gAj7fL8edg
Collei Demo 「Sprout in the Thicket」 Piano Performance : https://youtu.be/4_P8vIO2EXI
